In the infrastructure folder the api is created with endpoints and with integration of swagger.
This api is using the clean architecture

# Clean architecture

The clean architecture uses the layers Controller > usecase > entity
The idea is that comunication is only done from the outerlayers to inner and the inner layers do not communicate with the other layer.

1. In this project when the api recieves a call it entered in the controller
2. The data is then sent to the usercase where the
